fields.name: Premium Leather Collar
fields.description: Handcrafted genuine leather collar with adjustable buckle. Durable and comfortable for daily wear. Features soft padding for extra comfort.

fields.name: Reflective Safety Collar
fields.description: High-visibility reflective collar perfect for evening walks. Water-resistant and easy to clean. Available in multiple sizes.

fields.name: Retractable Dog Leash
fields.description: 16-foot retractable leash with one-button brake and lock. Ergonomic anti-slip handle for comfortable grip. Supports dogs up to 50kg.

fields.name: Heavy Duty Training Leash
fields.description: Professional-grade 6-foot training leash made from reinforced nylon. Perfect for obedience training and walking large dogs.

fields.name: Interactive Squeaky Ball
fields.description: Durable rubber ball with built-in squeaker. Perfect for fetch and play. Non-toxic and easy to clean. Suitable for all dog sizes.

fields.name: Rope Tug Toy
fields.description: Heavy-duty braided cotton rope toy for tug-of-war. Helps clean teeth and massage gums. Machine washable and long-lasting.

fields.name: Plush Chew Toy Set
fields.description: Set of 3 soft plush toys with squeakers inside. Perfect for gentle chewers. Cute animal designs your dog will love.

fields.name: Stainless Steel Food Bowl
fields.description: Dishwasher-safe stainless steel bowl with non-skid rubber base. Rust-resistant and hygienic. Available in small, medium, and large sizes.

fields.name: Elevated Double Bowl Stand
fields.description: Raised feeding station with two stainless steel bowls. Promotes better posture and digestion. Adjustable height for growing dogs.

fields.name: Automatic Water Fountain
fields.description: Electric pet water fountain with triple filtration system. Encourages hydration with flowing water. Ultra-quiet pump. 2L capacity.

fields.name: Memory Foam Dog Bed
fields.description: Orthopedic memory foam bed with removable washable cover. Perfect for senior dogs or those with joint issues. Non-slip bottom.

fields.name: Cozy Donut Bed
fields.description: Round plush donut-shaped bed with raised rim for head support. Super soft and comfortable. Machine washable. Multiple colors available.

fields.name: Outdoor All-Weather Bed
fields.description: Waterproof and UV-resistant elevated bed. Perfect for outdoor use. Breathable mesh center keeps dogs cool. Easy to clean.

fields.name: Waterproof Rain Jacket
fields.description: Lightweight waterproof jacket with reflective strips. Adjustable straps for perfect fit. Keeps your dog dry during rainy walks.

fields.name: Winter Fleece Sweater
fields.description: Warm and cozy fleece sweater for cold weather. Soft fabric with stretchy fit. Available in various sizes and colors. Easy to put on and take off.

fields.name: Cooling Vest
fields.description: Innovative cooling vest for hot summer days. Activated by water, provides hours of cooling relief. Lightweight and comfortable.

fields.name: Premium Dry Dog Food
fields.description: High-quality dry food with real chicken as the first ingredient. Balanced nutrition for adult dogs. Grain-free formula. 5kg bag.

fields.name: Puppy Formula Food
fields.description: Specially formulated nutrition for growing puppies. Contains DHA for brain development. Rich in protein and calcium. 3kg bag.

fields.name: Training Treat Pack
fields.description: Small, soft training treats perfect for positive reinforcement. Low calorie and easy to digest. Made with natural ingredients. 500g pack.

fields.name: Portable Travel Water Bottle
fields.description: Leak-proof travel water bottle with attached bowl. One-hand operation. Perfect for walks, hikes, and trips. 350ml capacity.

fields.name: Pet Grooming Kit
fields.description: Complete grooming set with brush, comb, nail clippers, and scissors. Professional-quality tools in a convenient carrying case.

fields.name: Pet First Aid Kit
fields.description: Comprehensive first aid kit for pets. Includes bandages, antiseptic, tweezers, and emergency guide. Essential for every pet owner.

fields.name: GPS Tracking Collar
fields.description: Smart GPS collar with real-time location tracking. Waterproof and rechargeable. Activity monitoring and geofencing features. Requires subscription.

fields.name: Dental Chew Toys Bundle
fields.description: Set of 4 dental chew toys designed to reduce plaque and tartar. Different textures and shapes. Promotes healthy teeth and gums.

fields.name: Luxury Pet Carrier Bag
fields.description: Stylish and comfortable airline-approved pet carrier. Padded shoulder strap and multiple ventilation windows. Perfect for small dogs and cats.
